messages.msg: Welcome to our site! If you are looking for prayer or someone to chat with, reply to this message or email us at prayer@fightlust.com
Hello! Welcome to FightLust.com! How can we support you in your journey towards healing today?
Absolutely! We are here to pray with you. Do you have a specific prayer request you'd like to share?
Deliverance from daydreaming and creating fake scenarios in my head and also for deliverance i keep dreaming am in filthy places all the time

Thank you for sharing your prayer request. Let's pray for your deliverance from daydreaming and the negative scenarios you're experiencing. 

Heavenly Father, we come before you today, asking for your strength and guidance. We pray for deliverance from daydreaming and the creation of false scenarios in our minds. We ask that you cleanse our thoughts and help us focus on what is pure and true. 

We also pray for freedom from the dreams that lead us to filthy places. Lord, we ask that you protect our minds during the night and fill our dreams with your peace and holiness. 

Thank you for your love and grace. In Jesus' name, we pray. Amen.

If you need further support or resources, feel free to let me know!
You're very welcome! If you need anything else or would like more prayers or support, just let me know. We're here for you!
Great! Take care, and remember that we're here to support you whenever you need it. Have a blessed day!
Good to know.Thank you very much and You too have a great day
Thank you! I appreciate your kind words. If you ever need support or have any questions, don't hesitate to reach out. Have a wonderful day!
Of course! I'm here to help. What questions do you have?
1.How do can one tell the difference between a vision and Imagination.

That's a thoughtful question! However, I don't have specific information on that topic. I recommend seeking guidance through prayer or discussing it with a trusted spiritual advisor who can provide insights based on biblical teachings. If you have more questions or need support, feel free to ask!
How can one overcome fear of commitment

I don't have specific information on overcoming the fear of commitment. It might be helpful to seek guidance through prayer and consider talking to a trusted friend or counselor who can provide support. If you have any other questions or need assistance, just let me know!
